RelatedSentence: MANILA , Philippines - Andrea Rosal , the daughter of the late New Peoples Army spokesperson Gregorio Ka Roger Rosal , on Monday asked the Pasig City Regional Trial Court Branch 266 to allow her to attend the wake of her baby daughter at the University of the Philippines in Diliman Tuesday and the infant 's burial in Ibaan , Batangas on Wednesday .

In a four - page urgent ex-parte motion filed before the court by her lawyers , Andrea sought the court 's permission saying that she remains distressed , devastated , and inconsolable and was not given the chance to see her daughter after she gave birth at the Philippine General Hospital last May 17 at about 8 a.m. Andrea 's baby daughter , Diona Andrea , died of hypoxemia ( low level of oxygen in the blood ) at around 5 p.m. the following day .
